SEARCH
Package nl.pim16aap2.bigdoors.core.structures

Class StructureSnapshot

java.lang.Object
nl.pim16aap2.bigdoors.core.structures.StructureSnapshot
All Implemented Interfaces:
IStructureConst
public final class StructureSnapshot extends Object implements IStructureConst
Represents a (read-only) snapshot of a structure at a particular point in time.

All access to this class is thread safe and does not lock.

Author:
Pim

    • getOpenDir

      public MovementDirection getOpenDir()
      Description copied from interface: IStructureConst
      Gets the MovementDirection this IStructure will open if currently closed.

      Note that if it's currently in the open status, it is supposed go in the opposite direction, as the closing direction is the opposite of the opening direction. This isn't taken into account by this method.

      Specified by:
      getOpenDir in interface IStructureConst
      Returns:
      The MovementDirection this IStructure will open in.
